  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dda \u0db6\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0da2\u0dbd\u0dba \u0d87\u0daf\u0dca\u0daf \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0da7 \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 10\u0d9a \u0daf\u0da9\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Millionaire fined 10 lakhs for drawing water from a girl in Galle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Water Supply and Water Transport Board, a millionaire business contractor has been fined nearly ten lakh rupees for illegally obtaining water from a free water supply line for a famous girls' college in Galle.",
        "Mr. Ekanayake Weerasinghe, Assistant General Manager (Charges) of the Water Supply and Drainage Board said that the fine was later paid by the businessman.",
        "This contractor is a builder of a school building. During an investigation by the Water Supply and Drainage Board, information has been revealed that he has been getting water for the construction of the building for some time from the free water supply to the school.",
        "Meanwhile, the Water Supply and Drainage Board has received information that some canteens, principal's and teachers' houses, swimming pools run for business purposes, etc., are getting water from the roads that provide free water to schools.",
        "The board states that it is keeping a close eye on this matter these days.",
        "Officials of the board point out that by misusing the free water provided to schools, the government incurs huge losses every year.",
        "Under the supervision of Mr. Ekanayake Weerasinghe, Assistant General Manager (Collection) of the Water Supply and Drainage Board, the commercial section of the Galle Regional Office of the Water Resources Board had worked to collect this fine."
      ],
